  "texts": [
    "Hence, the chance of success of timelines research is low.Its degree of beneficence is moderate.",
    "Knowledge about AI timelines is relevant for many kinds of decisions.",
    "First, 11 Some timelines research produces surveys in which putative experts are asked for their estimates of AI timelines [19,20].",
    "Yet, the skills required for AI research do not necessarily correlate with skills for long-term AI forecasting.",
    "Further, in the absence of a validated scientific procedure for forecasting AI progress, it is doubtful that anyone could be an expert AI forecaster.these systems could cause enormous damage if they pursue the wrong goals."
